data.description: Welcome to Pineapple Park at Woodmont! Come step inside this charming corner unit , a 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse spanning 1580 living sqft. On the first floor, you'll find tiled floors, a spacious living room, dining area, laundry, upgraded kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and beautiful countertops, and don't forget to step out on to the screened-in back patio for some fresh air. Upstairs, enjoy vinyl flooring and discover two master bedrooms, each with its own bathroom and walk-in closet, while he primary master suite goes the extra mile with not one but two walk-in closets. Property comes with 2 assigned parking spaces plus additional guest parking. Closet to community pool, sawgrass expressway, turnpike, restaurants, shops and more!
